If you've ever dreamed of getting away from it all with your own slice of paradise for idyllic holidays, then look no further. 

Tiny Dun Maraig - located just near the Isle of Skye - has a setting as beautiful as it is private and it has just gone on sale with a starting price of £10,000.

But you'll need to be happy to rough it as there are no modern amenities of any kind and it is barely the size of half a football pitch. 

