He added: 'I have seen photographs of my island. I am told it is easy to get to in a small boat.

'I am much looking forward to it. Maybe I can build a small house on the island and sit and admire the view.' 

Vladi Private Islands' portfolio includes deluxe islands befitting the rich and famous in the Caribbean and the Mediterranean, but doesn't have a lot to say about Dun Maraig. 

'A rocky structure, covered by grass; attentive owners may even find the remains of a fort if they look closely enough,' their promotional material states, before going on to wax lyrical about its surrounds. 

